    "slideTitle0": "Amazing Korean Basics",
    "slideDesc0": "Amazing Korean makes learning Korean easy.\nYou can understand Korean in any of 22 languages.\nAmazing Korean Basics is the first step to study TOPIK and EPS-TOPIK.\nFrom pronunciation to basic grammar, sentence structure, and 500 sentences to build your Korean foundation.",
